.\" vim: tw=72 fdm=marker cms=.\\"\ %s
.
.\" FRONT MATTER {{{
.Dd Aug 15, 2016
.Os
.Dt SMRT-FETCH 1
.
.Sh NAME
.Nm smrt\ fetch
.Nd Collect maintenance update metadata
.\" FRONT MATTER }}}
.
.\" SYNOPSIS {{{
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Fl h | \-help
.Nm
.Op Fl \-adopt
.Op Fl \-push
.Brq Ar MPRJ | MRID | SLUG
.Op Ar DEST
.\" SYNOPSIS }}}
.
.\" DESCRIPTION {{{
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
downloads and stores metadata for a maintenance update
from a BuildService instance API.
.\" }}}
.
.\" OPTIONS {{{
.Sh OPTIONS
.Bl -tag -width "xxx"
. It Fl \-adopt
Assign the maintenance request to yourself for testing.
Runs
.Nm osc Cm qam Cm assign Fl \-skip-template Ns .
. It Fl \-push
Run
.Nm smrt Cm push
on results of successful metadata acquisition.
.El
.\" }}}
.
.\" OPERANDS {{{
.Sh OPERANDS
.Bl -tag -width "xxx"
.It Ar MPRJ
. No See Sx OPERANDS No in Xr smrt 1 .
. Ar ISSUER
is queried for the outstanding maintenance request targetting
. Ar ISSUE
to derive
. Ar SLUG Ns .
.It Ar MRID
. No See Sx OPERANDS No in Xr smrt 1 .
. Sy Assumed Issuer
is queried for the
. Sy Maintenance Project
targetted by
. Ar MRID
to derive
. Ar SLUG Ns .
.It Ar SLUG
. No See Sx OPERANDS No in Xr smrt 1 .
Verify in
. Ar ISSUER
that
. Ar MRID
is the outstanding
. Sy Maintenance Request
for the
. Sy Maintenance Project
. Ar MPRJ Ns .
.It Ar DEST
Destination directory.
If the path exists it must be an empty directory.
Defaults to
. Ar SLUG Ns .
.El
.\" }}}
.
